{{Infobox sports award | name = Slam Dunk Contest | image = | image_size = | alt = | caption = | sport = [[Lietuvos krepšinio lyga]] | competition = | discipline = | givenfor = | english = | localnames = {{native name|lt|Oro Karalius}} | nickname = | first = [[Gary Arrington]], 1994 | number = | last = | first winner | mostwins = [[Darius Sirtautas]]: 3 times | mostrecent = [[Kenny Gaines]] | pastwinners = {{div col|colwidth=10em}}{{unbulleted list|1994 [[Gary Arrington]]|1995 [[Darius Sirtautas]]|1996 No contest held|1997 [[Darius Sirtautas]]|1998 [[Darius Sirtautas]]|1999 [[Eurelijus Žukauskas]]|2000 [[Robertas Javtokas]]|2001 [[Robertas Javtokas]]|2002 [[Dainius Šalenga]]|2003 [[Aaron Lucas]]|2004 [[Marco Spears]]|2005 [[Antonio Grant]]|2006 No contest held|2007 [[Aivaras Kiaušas]]|2008 [[Mantas Kalnietis]]|2009 [[Arvydas Šikšnius]]|2010 [[Aron Baynes]]|2011 [[Algirdas Palaima]]|2012 [[Sonny Weems]]|2013 [[Šarūnas Beniušis]]|2014 [[Travis Leslie]]|2015 [[Travis Leslie]]|2016 [[Rafal Lipinski]]|2017 [[Gediminas Žitlinskas]] |2018 [[Kenny Gaines]] }} {{Div col end}} | url = <!-- {{URL|example.com}} --> }}
The '''LKL Slam Dunk Contest''' is an annual [[Lietuvos krepšinio lyga|Lithuanian Basketball League]] (LKL) competition, that was originally held during the [[LKL All-Star Day]], and later during the [[Karaliaus Mindaugo taurė|King Mindaugas Cup]]. The contest has been held almost every year, from the first All-Star Day.
==History== Throughout the history of the contest, there have been witnessed many famous moments. Most noticeable being the 2001 contest, in [[Kaunas]], where [[Robertas Javtokas]] (representing [[BC Lietuvos rytas|Lietuvos rytas]]) repeated the World Record for the highest slam dunk, when he dunked a basketball on a goal set at 3.65m (12 feet) above the floor.<ref>{{cite news|title=Nuo rekordo iki kuriozo: įsimintiniausi LKL Žvaigždžių dienos dėjimai|url=http://www.alfa.lt/straipsnis/49962319/nuo-rekordo-iki-kuriozo-isimintiniausi-lkl-zvaigzdziu-dienos-dejimai|accessdate=18 February 2017|work=alfa.lt|date=4 January 2016|language=Lithuanian}}</ref>
The very first slam dunk contest was won by [[Gary Arrington]], of [[BC Statyba]], at the 1994 [[LKL All-Star Day]], in [[Panevėžys]].<ref name="History">{{cite news|last1=Ramoška|first1=Saulius|title=Rankas smailina tritaškininkai ir dėjikai|url=http://lzinios.lt/lzinios/Sportas/rankas-smailina-tritaskininkai-ir-dejikai/238960|accessdate=18 February 2017|work=Lietuvos žinios|date=18 February 2017|language=Lithuanian}}</ref> The current champion of the LKL Dunk Contest is [[Kenny Gaines]].<ref name="2017 konkursas">{{cite news|title=KMT „Oro karaliumi“ tapo A.Bestą nurungęs 175 cm ūgio G.Žitlinskas |url=http://www.krepsinis.net/naujiena/kmt-oro-karaliumi-tapo-a-besta-nurunges-175-cm-ugio-g-zitlinskas/270931 |accessdate=18 February 2017 |work=Krepsinis.net |date=18 February 2017 |language=Lithuanian}}</ref>
